Monday, May 2, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

93-2348. Cincinnati Bengals, Inc. v. Papania.

Hamilton County, No. C-920272. This cause is pending before the court on the filing of a motion for an order directing the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County to certify its record. Upon consideration of the joint motion for stay,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, effective April 29, 1994, that the motion for stay is moot as the court in its entry of April 21, 1994, stayed proceedings in this case until May 23, 1994.
